name: Moment of Truth
description:
Moment of Truth
Limited Edition Print of 100
Edition Status- New Release!

Paper Size- 56 x 56cm
Image Size- 50 x 50cm

Printed with archival inks on Hahnemühle fine art paper. Hand signed, titled and numbered by Joel Rea. Delivered by Australia Post Registered Mail in a custom hard tube.

$220 includes postage and packaging for Australia only. An additional $30 for International shipping. Allow 2-3 weeks for delivery.


Steps to Purchase-

1. Add item to Cart
2. Click Cart on left hand side to checkout
3. Pay using PayPal or with Credit/Debit Card.
